</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Police are asking for help in locating a private security guard reported 
missing by his family since July 26. 
</P>
<P>
 Michael Jerome Williams, 32, left his home in the 3700 block of South Van Ness 
Street 10 days ago to pick up uniforms and has not returned or contacted his 
family, said Santa Ana Police Sgt. Dick Faust. 
</P>
