pounds, Faust said. He is missing two front teeth. He has brown eyes and short 
hair, and was last seen wearing a white T-shirt. Williams has no known medical 
or mental problems. Anyone with information regarding his whereabouts is asked 
to contact Santa Ana police at (714) 834-4801, or Investigator B. Rodriguez. 
