<TEXT>
<P>
 Documents carried by a suspect in a wave of bombings that killed more than 300 
in Bombay last year show that Pakistan was involved, India's home affairs 
minister said.Top suspect Yakub Abdul Razak Memon was arrested in New Delhi. 
Indian Home Affairs Minister S.B. Chavan said documents recovered from Memon 
