<P>
 Fighting preventable childhood diseases will be the focus of the fifth annual 
Kids Care Fair scheduled for Aug. 27.  
</P>
<P>
 Local organizations, businesses and volunteers will participate in the fair, 
similar to others being held at more than 40 locations in five Southern 
California counties. 
</P>
<P>
