</P>
<P>
 Heat 1 -- Richie Collins, Newport Beach (22.60); 2. Gary Elkerton, France 
(21.30). Heat 2 -- 1. Stuart Bedford Brown, Australia (24.04); 2. Jake Spooner, 
Australia (22.07). Heat 3 -- 1. Sunny Garcia, Waianae, Hawaii (23.04); 2. Vetea 
David, Brazil (22.79). Heat 4 -- 1. Todd Holland, Cocoa Beach, Fla. (26.36); 2. 
