 Sunrise Little League of Woodland Hills has scheduled player registration for 
Aug. 20, 27 and Sept. 3 from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. Players between the ages of 5 
and 12 are eligible. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: 818-883-3038. Softball 
</P>
