 The Oxnard Mermaids, a slow-pitch team for girls 16 and under, won two games 
and lost three at a national tournament sponsored by the Pony softball 
organization. 
</P>
<P>
 The three-day tournament in Round Rock, Tex., drew 60 teams from across the 
country. 
